Instead of defining this constant, you could consider to use TimeUnit.SECONDS.toMilliseconds(1) as an in-line constant - or atlernately, use a semantic label, like:
private static final int MAX_SUBSCRIPTION_FAILURE_TIME_MS = TimeUnit.SECONDS.toMillseconds(1);

which sort of achieves two purposes of documentation - how long it is, and what it purpose is

